title: The Average Apple User
description: If you use this laptop, you're an average DePauw student. Pretty basic honestly. There's nothing much to say. You do think Apple is better than Android though.
creator: Apple

title: The Deluxe Apple User
description: If you have a PC in your dorm, this is some next level pretentiousness. Was a laptop not enough for you to flex?
creator: Apple

title: The Trusty Old Laptop
description: These laptops are being used since your highschool, or is probably a hand-me-down. Either way, it showcases true Gold Commitment
creator: Dell

title: The International's Favorite
description: HP laptops are becoming an international student's favorite. You might spot one everytime you go to UB. These users are a little less basic than the Mac users, but basic nonetheless.
creator: HP

title: The Fancy iPads
description: Another cult favorite of DePauw, it is becoming clear that society is progressing pass the need for a laptop entirely. If you use this instead of an actual laptop, safe bet is you probably aren't a CS major
creator: Apple

title: I Broke My Laptop
description: The title says it all. You're probably only here because you're in crisis mode.
